snippet.title: Abode Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on steam here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/548340/

In Abode you'll visit a Sci-fi noir apartment.
Inspired by "escape the room" games.

You will pick up, inspect, open, repair or utilize objects or furniture in the room in order to unveil all it's secrets.

HTC Vive Exclusive.
